data.description: Come see this well cared for one owner home near the heart of Oro Valley and minutes to Oro Valley CC. Wonderful views of Pusch Ridge from this east facing one story home on a corner lot.  Many upgrades when built and over the years. Enter the living room with vaulted ceilings and saltillo tile floors that also flow into the den. Enjoy the comfy family room open to the kitchen & mid-west style Brick fireplace, bay windows in breakfast nook, french doors out to a wrap around yard with brick pavers leading to the front yard. Newer 2016 low E windows throughout the home some with plantation shutters. HVAC 09/2015, Samsung Gas Range 2014, GE SS side by side Fridge & GE washer 2022. Fully paid Solar/Gas water heater 2012. Dishwasher 2012. Garage has extra width and built in storage cabinets.
